 architecture-heavy but not yet balanced toward governance-aware architect scope.","supported_by":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:123","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:163","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:250","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:266"],"citation":"These bullets better express the target category’s stakeholder-and-governance pattern."},{"priority_rank":5,"action":"Rebalance the skills block away from tool-list density alone and surface architecture terms such as AI architecture, solutions architecture, governance, stakeholder management, observability, CI/CD, and monitoring when backed by the curated evidence.","section":"skills","why_now":"Current skills emphasize retrieval tooling more than category-defining architecture and delivery vocabulary.","supported_by":["data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:10","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:163","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:250"],"citation":"The category rewards architecture and delivery framing over tool laundry lists."}],"evidence_ledger":[{"recommendation":"Lead the category baseline with production AI platform architecture and RAG-centered delivery.","classification":"supported_and_curated","support":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:7"],"confidence":"high"},{"recommendation":"Use governance-aware deployment as a core differentiator through privacy/compliance and GenAI guardrails.","classification":"supported_and_curated","support":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:106","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:9"],"confidence":"high"},{"recommendation":"Frame leadership as player-coach mentoring and architectural guidance, not executive managemen